  "system": {
    "subType": "mutation",
    "description": "<p>You can instinctively modulate the light level around you. You can create visible light within a 10-meter radius or shroud up to a 2-meter radius in inky darkness that resists all illumination. While shrouded, you gain an Armor Class bonus of +2 due to your obfuscation. You can see normally regardless of the light level around you. When you or an ally within 10 meters are hit by a laser weapon, accept one System Strain as an Instant action to negate the damage.</p>",
